{"tid":1563140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(緊急)大家要唱埋美國國歌，唔好淨係唱香港國歌","createTime":"2019-09-12T09:50:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T16:18:13.000Z","uid":131157,"like":58,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"085c7633bb972d859722e11509951b12fbdf1ea0","tid":1563140,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:50:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n據聞美國只需一位參議員提出senate hold，只要全體不足三分二反對，香港人權及民主法案即可在參議會上無限期擱置，直至有關議員收回動議。<br />\n<br />\n假如屬實，中國將全力收買部份參議員，企圖促成法案流產。與此同時，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">在香港營造萬人普天同慶唱流行曲的氣氛，將上周高舉美國國旗</span></span></strong>、<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唱美國國歌的勢頭消散於無形。</span></strong>只要香港人不再強烈請求美國支援，而香港事態不會影響美國的民主，美國將不會有動力以狠辣的法案監察香港。屆時，民意代表泛民議員將有充分的理由建議美國減辣，以免在局勢緩和的時候傷害香港經濟。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">只要未來兩周，香港人繼續以所謂香港國歌取代美國國歌的話，將美國角色隱沒至大後方的話，美國減辣的機會相當高。要保持辣度</span></strong>，必需仰賴美國議員極具說服力論證，非常困難。香港人將自己的好牌一張張的送出，無話可說。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10157187675233880&amp;id=700268879\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10157187675233880%26id%3D700268879&d=S%2BP5iCTdX9iTDztVuYOIbzyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=dabd5622\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10157187675233880&amp;id=700268879</a>"},{"pid":"701389755947f54e9fafbabc13fc5366a560511a","tid":1563140,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:50:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf74b7f6babde0675956bd77376a0b1bd56b609","tid":1563140,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep